               stealing, on the <rs id="t18281023-237-cd1378" type="crimeDate">14th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18281023-237-off1377 t18281023-237-cd1378"></join>, 2 fur tippets, value 3l.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18281023-237-victim1253" type="victimName">
                  Jacob 
                  Harris
               <interp inst="t18281023-237-victim1253" type="surname" value="Harris"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18281023-237-victim1253" type="given" value="Jacob"></interp>
